The Trello Harvest Info Extension is a Chrome extension designed to enhance your Trello experience by providing additional Harvest data on your Trello boards. With this extension, you can view detailed information about your Trello cards.

Features:
- See time spent on each card
- How long ago the card was made
- The number of cards in each column
